<TEXTAREA NAME="Text" COLS="60" ROWS="6" WRAP="VIRTUAL">here's a profile list on each of them, including the ones not mentioned in the previous subject.

Crimson-(That's me)
Description- Red with green eyes, and blue sneakers
Relation- Sonic's brother

Lime-
Description- gren, also with green eyes and yellow sneakers.
relation- Sonic's sister

Michelle-
description- Reddish brown with ed sneakers
relation- Tails' twin sis'

Kerry-
description- light purple with multi colored sneakers
relation- Knux's sis'

Azure(M) and Viridian(F)-
description- same as the colors of their names, Azure blue and viridian purple.
relation- sonic's parents

Kiro- sky blue, female, hedgehog
relation- friend

Dansm- Brown, male, hedgehog
relation- friend

Ranu- Black, male, hedgehog
relation- friend

Jerry- white, female, hedgehog
relation- friend

Ward- pale Aquamarine, male, hedgehog
relation- friend

Jay- Silver, male, hedgehog
relation- friend

S jr.- can you guess what the &quot;S&quot; stands for? that's right world, say hello to sonic junior!

Sapphire- S jr.'s twin sister, only a lighter shade of blue

Tykon- Let me see, he's an echidna, he's red, and he's a year younger than S jr., so that must mean... Knux's son!

Spike- Bassically, spike is Knuckles' other long lost relative, but they don't exactly get along well. I wonder why? Black with purple gloves, purple eyes, and his crescent moon shape is red instead of white.

Skilos- Silver blue, red gloves, a leather jacket, and brass knuckles to acompany his real ones. ouch. Used to belong to the Black Ribbon gang, not anymore, but he still wears their trademark black ribbons on his spines. His name is an alteration of the greek word skliros, meaning Tough.

Mekka- Doesn't his name say it all? Purple, robotic arms, robotic head(Except for the eyes and nose) and a robotic leg. And I say again, ouch. wears a brown trench coat.

Gen. James Khan- The leader of GUN's special task force, he's still after Sonic and friends. But are his motives as dark as they seem? Green with brown eyes, brown leather jacket.

Kinidos- The desert bounty hunter, he sports twin swords and a bad attitude. He is dark orange with red stripes all across his body. wears an orange trench coat. his name comes from an alteration of the greek word kynigos, meaning hunter.

The Entity- the ultimate fighter, totally green eyes, blue with red on the edges, and huge fists with spikes. can you guess who is part of him? I'll tell you one: Chaos 0

Metallica- basically, she's a female version of Metal Sonic. In a way, you could call her Metal Amy. In a way.

That about wraps it up for characters, and to answer your question, I don't know how I come up with em' all.
